{"seq":32,"timestamp":"2026-05-11T23:20:04.214601483Z","actor":"ag_ui_user","phase":"user_request","direction":"incoming","method":"text_message_content","content":{"messageId":"5623092a-0494-48a6-a4e0-81acbc6396a9","delta":"# Q1 Sales Data Analysis — Results\n\nI delegated the Q1 sales analysis task to the **DataAnalyticsAgent**. Here's a summary of what happened:\n\n## Agent Response\nThe **DataAnalyticsAgent (v1.0.0)** at `https://analytics-agent.example.com` processed the request and returned:\n\n> **\"Analysis complete.\"**\n\nThe agent reported a `completed` status, meaning it successfully finished the task on its end.\n\n## Key Findings\nUnfortunately, the agent returned only a brief status message with no detailed analysis output. This could mean:\n\n1. **The agent processed the data server-side** — The full analysis (totals, monthly breakdowns, trends, etc.) may be available in the agent's own dashboard or output stream, which wasn't returned via this A2A interface.\n2. **Streaming was enabled** (`streaming=true`) — The agent supports streaming, but the detailed results may not have been captured in this synchronous response.\n3. **No local data file was found** — I searched `/home/user/`, `/data/`, `/tmp/`, and the working directory for files like `q1_sales.csv`, `q1_sales_data.csv`, and `sales_q1.csv` but didn't find a Q1 sales dataset locally. The agent likely has its own data store.\n\n## Recommended Next Steps\n- **Check the agent's dashboard** at `https://analytics-agent.example.com` for the full report.\n- **Re-run with explicit parameters** — If you can share the Q1 sales CSV data here, I can provide a direct analysis.\n- **Verify the agent's streaming output** — Since streaming is supported, the detailed results may be in a streamed channel.\n\nWould you like me to try a different approach or help with anything else?"}}
